.TH mkdirhier "" "" "X Utility"
.PC "Make a directory hierarchy"
\fBmkdirhier \fIdirectory ...\fR
.PP
The X utility
.B mkdirhier
creates each
.IR directory .
Unlike the \*(CO command
.BR mkdir ,
.B mkdirhier
creates any of the parent directories of
.I directory
if do not exist.
.SH "See Also"
.B
X utilities
.R
.br
\*(CO Lexicon:
.B
mkdir
.R
